    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This could happen if you are not running the command prompt in administrator mode. \nIf you are using windows 7, you can go to run, type cmd and hit Ctrl+Shift+enter. This will open the command prompt in administrator mode. If not, you can also go to start -> all programs -> accessories -> right click command prompt and click 'run as administrator'. </p>\n"
