    "answer_id" : 36052951,
    "question_id" : 10321211,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you are using windows8:</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>Click start button</li>\n<li>In the search box, type <code>command prompt</code></li>\n<li>From the result, right-click <code>command prompt</code> and click <code>Run as administrator</code>. Then execute the keytool command.</li>\n</ol>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 8424768,
      "reputation" : 39,
      "user_id" : 6322431,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/17b7ad47c3f623731045f26fd7007955?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "goyalshub1509",
