      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Note %JAVA%/jre/lib/security is correct only for Java 8 and below -- and only if you installed JDK and not separate JRE, but that&#39;s likely as SO users are supposedly developers. Java 9 (current when this A was posted) and above are only %JAVA%/lib/security ."
