    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Make sure you running as Administrator.\nIn Mac terminal:-</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Run sudo -i</li>\n<li>Then execute the commands</li>\n</ol>\n"
