    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Our keystore was stored in SCM, and for some reason downloading the file directly from the SCM service again, enabled modifying the keystore.  Probably the earlier download of the file didn't bring it in binary format.</p>\n"
